Events from the year '''1713 in Ireland'''.
==Events==
*November&ndash;December – [[Parliament of Ireland]] meets and is [[prorogued]] without voting [[Appropriation bill|supply]] beyond the end of the year.
* [[Dublin election riot]] - A riot broke out in [[Dublin]] during the contested election of the [[Dublin City (Parliament of Ireland constituency)|Dublin City]] constituency by the [[Whigs (British political party)|Whigs]] and [[Tories]].

