{{Infobox Bilateral relations|Bolivia–Russia|Bolivia|Russia|filetype=svg}} [[File:Vladimir Putin and Evo Morales (2018-06-13) 03.jpg|thumb|right|[[President of Bolivia|President]] Morales meeting with [[Russian President]] [[Vladimir Putin]] in [[Moscow Kremlin]] on June 2018.]]
'''Bolivia–Russia relations''' ({{lang-ru|Российско-боливийские отношения}}) is the relationship between the two countries, [[Bolivia]] and [[Russia]]. Russia has an [[embassy]] in [[La Paz]], and Bolivia has an [[Embassy of Bolivia in Moscow|embassy in Moscow]].
== Country comparison == {| class="wikitable" style="text-align:center" |- ! style="width:12em;" scope="col" | ! style="width:25em;" scope="col" | Bolivia ! style="width:25em;" scope="col" | Russia |- ! scope="row" | Population | 10,027,254 (2012)<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ine.gob.bo:8081/censo2012/PDF/resultadosCPV2012.pdf | title=Bolivia: Características de Población y Vivienda: Censo National de Población y Vivienda 2012 | publisher=Bolivian National Institute of Statistics | page=4 | accessdate=21 September 2014 | language=Spanish | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209134921/http://www.ine.gob.bo:8081/censo2012/PDF/resultadosCPV2012.pdf | archivedate=9 February 2014 | df= }}</ref> | 143,800,000 (2014) <ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20140725175529/http://www.gks.ru/bgd/free/B14_00/IssWWW.exe/Stg//%3Cextid%3E/%3Cstoragepath%3E%3A%3A%7Cdk06/8-0.doc ]</ref> |- ! scope="row" | Area | 1,098,581&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup> (2012)<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ine.gob.bo:8081/censo2012/PDF/resultadosCPV2012.pdf | title=Bolivia: Características de Población y Vivienda: Censo National de Población y Vivienda 2012 | publisher=Bolivian National Institute of Statistics | page=5 | accessdate=21 September 2014 | language=Spanish | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209134921/http://www.ine.gob.bo:8081/censo2012/PDF/resultadosCPV2012.pdf | archivedate=9 February 2014 | df= }}</ref> | 17,098,242&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup> (2014)<ref name="RUcia">{{cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/rs.html|title=The World Factbook|website=Cia.gov|accessdate=15 April 2016}}</ref> |- ! scope="row" | Density | {{Decimals|{{#expr:10027254/1098581}}|2}}/km<sup>2</sup> (2012) | {{Decimals|{{#expr:142470272/17098242}}|2}}/km<sup>2</sup> (2014) |- ! scope="row" | Capital(s) | [[La Paz]], [[Sucre]] | [[Moscow]] |- ! scope="row" | Largest city | [[Santa Cruz de la Sierra]] (1.719 million, 2011)<ref>{{cite web | url=http