{{Italic title}}
'''Finnboga saga ramma''' ({{Audio|Is-Finnboga saga ramma.oga|listen}}) is an [[Icelandic saga]] that recounts the life of Finnbogi hinn rammi. The story takes place in [[Flateyjardalur]] in Suður-Þingeyjarsýsla and in other places in [[Iceland]], as well as in [[Norway]]. The events supposedly took place in the 10th century.

