'''Góry Trzebiatowskie''' {{IPAc-pl|'|g|u|r|y|-|t|sz|e|b|j|a|'|t|o|f|s|k|J|e}} is a [[village]] in the administrative district of [[Gmina Mniszków]], within [[Opoczno County]], [[Łódź Voivodeship]], in central Poland.<ref name="TERYT">{{cite web |url=http://www.stat.gov.pl/broker/access/prefile/listPreFiles.jspa |title=Central Statistical Office (GUS) - TERYT (National Register of Territorial Land Apportionment Journal) |date=2008-06-01 |language=Polish}}</ref> It lies approximately {{convert|6|km|mi|0}} north of [[Mniszków, Łódź Voivodeship|Mniszków]], {{convert|20|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} west of [[Opoczno]], and {{convert|55|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} south-east of the regional capital [[Łódź]].

