The '''Roman Catholic Diocese of Port-Gentil''' ({{lang-la|Portus Gentil(is)}}) is a [[diocese]] located in the city of [[Port-Gentil]] in the [[Ecclesiastical province]] of [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Libreville|Libreville]] in [[Gabon]].
